data.description: This home has it all!  Explore this enchanting Bob Chatham Custom Home Designs Craftsman, Gold-Fortified home in Gulf Shores, AL, the fastest growing city in Alabama based on the last census!  This charming, one-of-a-kind property is 1.5 miles from the new state of the art Gulf Shores High School, set to open in 2025. FEATURING:  Natural gas appliances--a Kohler all-home generator, Rinnai tankless hot water heater, Kitchen-Aid dual fuel range,  and a 36” Cal Flame inset outdoor grill; charming shiplap in foyer, kitchen, and dining area and foyer has a powder room; first level includes a family area, kitchen, master ensuite, a walk-in under-the-staircase storage closet, and a laundry closet; master ensuite includes cellular shades/custom blackout roller shades, double basin granite vanity, chandelier, barn door bathroom entry, custom step-in soaker tub, separate 6’ “tiled to the ceiling” shower with three custom shower heads, and a custom master closet (includes two built-in clothes hampers and a locked drawer for valuables); first level also has impressive 10’ ceilings, vinyl plank flooring, remote control ceiling fans, cellular shades, granite countertops, custom pantry with granite countertop, ceramic farmhouse single basin sink, custom, elegant lighting, and recessed lights for additional lighting; second level features comfortable 9’ ceilings, remote control ceiling fans, contemporary carpeting, landing space, two additional bedrooms, and an additional bathroom.  The landing area, bathroom, and bedrooms include foam insulated walk-in attic closets.  The outdoor space includes an outdoor kitchen with a gas grill, granite countertops, stainless steel drawers/cabinets, solar lighting, custom deck w/ cable railing for an amazing view of the wetlands, an outdoor custom firepit, waterline rip rock for erosion prevention, and natural landscape for lot delineation.  Community pool!
